description: Welcome to this exceptional penthouse triplex in the highly sought-after East Side of South Boston. This 3 bed, 2 bath home offers stunning panoramic ocean views and boasts outdoor decks on every floor, providing the perfect spaces to relax and entertain. The state-of-the-art kitchen is a chefs dream, featuring ample cabinet space, premium appliances, and luxurious granite countertops. The dining and living areas are designed for sophisticated gatherings, with soaring 9.5-foot ceilings, large bay windows that flood the space with natural light, and custom built-ins that add an elegant touch. The property's location exceptional, just a leisurely stroll away from the renowned Southie beaches, M Street, Carson, and Castle Island, as well as local dining and shopping venues. This home embodies the charm and feel of a Back Bay brownstone, but with the added allure of the beautiful coast of South Boston. This property is where you can experience the best of both coastal and city living!
